The set of programs in this directory integrate Vector with the OpenAI CLIP library

Details about OpenAI CLIP are available at: https://github.com/openai/CLIP

To run these programs, in addition to installing the anki_vector package, please do the following steps...

1. Clone CLIP from https://github.com/openai/CLIP
2. Install the dependencies for CLIP by the following instructions...
   a. conda install --yes -c pytorch pytorch=1.7.1 torchvision cpuonly
   b. pip install ftfy regex tqdm
3. Run the program as follows:
   python detectPicture.py --serial 0080230c -c "football,plush football"
   
